data.description: Take a look at this beautiful single-story home. It underwent a complete renovation in 2022, giving it a fresh and modern look. These renovations include: flooring, interior and exterior paint, windows, roof, garage, gas water heater, covered porch and patio, fence, stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry and much more. The spacious layout provides plenty of room for relaxation and enjoyment. With updated features and a stylish design, this home is move-in ready. It is conveniently located- minutes from major highways, shopping and entertainment. Schedule your showing today!
